query:
SELECT bc.totalBodyFatPct, bc.totalFatMass, bc.totalLeanMass, bc.totalMass, bc.vatArea, ds.scanDate 
FROM dexa_body_comp bc 
JOIN dexa_scans ds ON bc.scanId = ds.id 
WHERE ds.clientId = 630001 AND ds.status = 'approved' 
ORDER BY ds.scanDate DESC LIMIT 1\G
